{"tid":939721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE《TT》遭禁播！　「有猥褻含義」嚇壞菲律賓人","createTime":"2018-12-13T10:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T23:37:27.000Z","uid":74065,"like":223,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"77359cf81bdba1e8634ab1a9ae4833b551e1c893","tid":939721,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團TWICE由8位外表甜美、可愛的女孩組成，不只紅遍日、韓、台，就連在東南亞都有相當高的人氣。然而，她們的夯曲《TT》在菲律賓其實有另一種18禁含義，歌曲在當地禁播，此事，在菲律賓活動的韓星Ryan Bang證實：「雖然不是禁曲，但根本就不能在電視上播！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3760/d3760960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3760%2Fd3760960.jpg&h=d28b2433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「TT」在菲律賓是指男生的生殖器</span></strong></span>。（圖／翻攝自Youtube、MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3760/d3760956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3760%2Fd3760956.jpg&h=2d691171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於TT的發音在菲律賓是指男性生殖器，TWICE所唱的《TT》幾乎是整首歌的重點，在當地引起廣大討論，Ryan Bang證實：「不是禁曲，根本就是不能在電視上播！」如果有人在路上忽然高唱「TT」，手指還剛好指向下體，絕對會嚇壞當地人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3760/d3760955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3760%2Fd3760955.jpg&h=a3e61692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼主持人聽聞該消息嚇傻，編舞者也直呼「我不知道」。（圖／翻攝自MBC<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3760/d3760957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3760%2Fd3760957.jpg&h=e1c311ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當天節目上，《TT》的編舞老師Lia Kim喊冤表示，不知道有這個含義，「我純粹只是因為TT的手勢編舞，這樣看來，確實有點像在指下面（下體）的感覺，我錯了。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nI LKIE TT JUST LIKE TT</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dedf00c2e34343b4718d66b507cf4ccdbcf53a","tid":939721,"uid":213300,"like":115,"dislike":10,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"笑左笑撚埋右<br />\n洗唔洗禁埋香蕉"},{"pid":"4521f37f88ab2aa15a5ad0fec4ee95bcf9425a53","tid":939721,"uid":136738,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"l like TT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c317a0201ede566f54737bdc51d77dbcb6b93b","tid":939721,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> gay"},{"pid":"cc28125e400c9677966dd1aea3757d7f876c6ce6","tid":939721,"uid":74065,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"我TT好長"},{"pid":"d1cb47c71e79e10a02dfd3f8297292cbdbc386c3","tid":939721,"uid":42364,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"TT即係deedee"},{"pid":"b5b70fc4ae2794e8111a242e2fa1de0dc3dff080","tid":939721,"uid":123989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"8位?"},{"pid":"9599c1cd3d167a3e8385265710778aea953b1bb2","tid":939721,"uid":41508,"like":70,"dislike":4,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7705fb340bb27972e297d84c3123444162feda54","tid":939721,"uid":11208,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"77359cf81bdba1e8634ab1a9ae4833b551e1c893","tid":939721,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"